Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:02.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let the girl go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:04.40,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.94,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter Senbonzakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:09.82,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.49,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:16.70,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.00,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Scene 28, action!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.63,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:57.93,B2,MALE WALLA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:01:59.48,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say you're\Ngoing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:02.38,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost New Year's\Nmovie season!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.24,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Although the great\NHeisei recession,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.30,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,the so-called "lost decade" of\Nthe 90's, had come and gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.97,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,various financial crises occurred\Njust as people thought
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.49,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,that things were finally\Nstarting to look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:14.51,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,As people tightened their\Nwallets from spending,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:17.86,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,people sought low-cost\Nentertainment and began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,flocking to movie theaters\Non their long vacations
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.91,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,and spent their money there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.91,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,It behooves us not to get\Nleft behind by that trend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are the Thirteen Court Guard\NSquads that short on funds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.19,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,From what I heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.14,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,there apparently were\Nconsiderable expenditures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:36.69,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,to repair the damage to Seireitei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.92,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,caused by repeated emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That's because nobody thinks\Nabout the damage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.35,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,to their surroundings\Nwhen they fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.10,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,And so we have decided\Nto hold a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.71,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,"Seireitei International\NFilm Festival,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:53.10,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,celebrating the release\Nof Bleach Movie 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.54,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,The release of Bleach Movie 4?\NWhat the hell is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.12,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:03.30,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make an awesome movie\Nand wow everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's do our best,\NRenji, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.58,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why am I included?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all this enthusiasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And where did all this equipment\Ncome from anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.22,B2,REAPER A,0000,0000,0000,,Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:36.17,B2,POSTER,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Seireitei International\NFilm Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.13,B2,POSTER CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Co-sponsored\Nby Urahara's Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.05,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So it's from him, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.54,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he supposed to be\Nbanned from Seireitei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.17,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Unohana...and Komamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.12,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys filming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:04:00.25,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Squads 4 and 7 are working\Ntogether to make a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:03.01,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.50,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,It's a moving drama about\Nanimals saving human lives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.97,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,in a world where disasters\Nhave destroyed civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:13.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Animals? You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.32,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.16,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no... How should I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't quite fit the image.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.34,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.36,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I thought the costume
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.40,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't as well-made as\Nit could have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.05,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Please don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.92,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,It's because my acting\Nisn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.96,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for hindering\Nthe production!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.12,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,All right Tetsuzaemon, then I shall\Nteach you how to act better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.48,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.62,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:56.05,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should ask Squad\N12 for some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:56.48,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Captain, should I do that\Nwith my right hand, or left?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:59.21,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kurotsuchi did\Nsay he was preparing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.72,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hmm... Let's try\Nit with the right. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.63,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.32,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.78,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,full-body costumes for\Nhis special effects film.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.21,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.78,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Urr... Let me try\Nit again, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:02.41,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,A special effects film\Nby Squad 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:03.65,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.13,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We need to get\Nour timing right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You sure they're using\Nfull-body costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:06.78,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.88,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This time we'll try\Nwith the left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.02,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.51,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay, woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.27,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:09.49,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:09.84,B2,IBA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.45,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:16.14,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you mind playing\Na part in our movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.85,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,We're short on actors and\Ncould use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:26.72,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,We're short on actors and\Ncould use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.22,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks very good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Isn't this a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.99,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll be doing scene 15,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:42.07,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,the fight scene between the main\Ncharacter and the human
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.34,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,who was turned into a dog-man\Nby the curse of the dead dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of scene is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.17,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What? That you, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kenpachi! What are\Nyou doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.96,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,We're making a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:07.13,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,We in Squad 11 are making a blockbuster\Nmovie starring our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.93,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's an action flick where the\Ncaptain cuts down anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.39,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,and everything, including people,\Npoles, and even worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.81,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,And what's more, it's a documentary\Nwhere nothing is faked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.89,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Will that work as a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.65,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Just the man I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:31.49,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I had the urge to cut down\Nsomeone tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.12,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,So fight me for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.95,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.68,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,You saying you can't fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.28,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:50.09,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is currently occupied\Nwith our film.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:54.10,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go along with your\Nplans without our consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.25,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Unohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.67,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, we'll fight later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.58,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:14.33,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.16,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.37,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.24,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's get\Nback to filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.78,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:36.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness that's\Nfinally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.31,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake! Kyoraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.00,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.96,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,You look beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because\NUnohana insisted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I participate in the filming\Nof Squad 4's movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.24,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,That must've been rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:59.96,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys making a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.84,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was all for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:06.25,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,and even submitted a proposal,\Nbut Nanao here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.70,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,I will not approve of any\Nfilms rated "adults only"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.96,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of movie were\Nyou planning to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.64,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being filmed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:23.39,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro and Kiyone are making\Na documentary film
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.97,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,about me living life to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.78,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's to leave behind\Nfor future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.67,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.38,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.51,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a bit dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.53,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.45,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.31,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Quit wandering around, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.92,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We were ready to start\Nfilming ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care, Ukitake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.05,B2,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:53.70,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to your\Nfinished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.68,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia?! What's with the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.07,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.79,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is the star of our movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:09.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just what sort of movie are you\Nplanning to make with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.66,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "Battle Maid Cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.91,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the Soul Society\Nfrom Space Invaders!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.29,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I am Rukia, the Maid Cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.89,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So why the hell is she\Ndressed as a maid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:31.34,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We incorporated the latest trend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We can't attract moviegoers\Nif we don't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.84,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,incorporate the latest\Ntrends, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.24,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,\Nwe asked Rangiku to play
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.50,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,the role of the Maid Cop's rival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.40,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,the lovely criminal\Nfrom outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.47,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.61,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,And your role will be the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.75,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,mysterious High School Soul Reaper\Nwho comes to Rukia's rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That's no different from real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.69,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,And these are the members\Nof the Abarai Gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.21,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are we\Ndoing, Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:00.23,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I came because they asked\Nme to come if I was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:00.74,B2,SHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Muh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:05.06,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue will play the role of the human\Nunder Rangiku's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:08.00,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Chad, you'll be our gofer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.17,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be in charge of the\Ncostume design, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder the maid and alien\Nare both wearing capes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.55,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, you'll also be\Nour cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.14,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! I almost forgot someone\Nvery important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.82,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:31.23,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,The captain will be in charge\Nof visual effects using kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:36.43,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,The Seireitei's honor hangs on\Nthe Film Festival's success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:40.95,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore it is mandatory for all captains\Nto participate in this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.58,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's begin before\Nit gets dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:50.70,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Scene 62!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:53.26,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,In this scene, Ichigo rescues Rukia,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.22,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,who is about to be executed\Nby Chad and Inoue
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.59,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,who are under Rangiku's control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.88,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.48,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I get a scene\Nright from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.42,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.60,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I supposed\Nto be the gofer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.87,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're the director?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.81,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Here's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:15.09,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is captured after falling\Nfor Rangiku's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.37,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,And Ichigo can't do anything\Nsince Inoue and Chad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.99,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,are under Rangiku's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.66,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you're in a\Ndesperate situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.73,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You rescue Rukia. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.83,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.01,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Figure that out yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.17,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Places, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.24,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I'll leave the visual\Neffects up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.84,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Please make it look dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.24,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.51,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:50.37,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That is cowardly, space\Ncriminal Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.39,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,That is the whimpering of a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.27,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,If you're frustrated, try getting\Nyourself out of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,This will not make me lose heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.91,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure my friends will come\Nto rescue me at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.89,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over for you by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.62,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Finish her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.13,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.74,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.36,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.08,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, she has\Nus under her control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.64,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, that's not what\Nyou're supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.36,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,to say while under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.23,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.58,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I am in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:32.10,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to the\Nfate of the Maid Cop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.65,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.57,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let the girl go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:44.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I, Ichigo Kurosaki, the High School\NSoul Reaper will take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:49.08,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, for someone who was reluctant,\Nyou're really into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.45,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Say that after you see\Nthe situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.85,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I have hostages, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:13:01.05,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Can you harm people\Nfrom this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.12,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.42,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,She has us under her control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:06.01,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Muh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.77,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kill this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.73,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do\Nin this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.87,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Just attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.54,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your directions\Nare so general.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.65,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Muh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.53,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.28,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,El Directo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.41,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.54,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,It needs to look more\Nexciting than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.34,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki, please do your thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.36,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.84,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! Put your hands out in\Nfront and take your stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.27,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.96,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Just a pose will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.77,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:54.22,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 33: Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:01.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.15,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 4: Byakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.89,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why is your aim so accurate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one I'm fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.12,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Chad! What're you waiting\Nfor?! Continue attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.04,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.98,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,El Directo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.76,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter Senbonzakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.63,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.67,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do such\Na thing to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:45.92,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hold back even if you\Nare people of this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.90,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! Chad! Now drop\Nto the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.44,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, she got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.36,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Muh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.46,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Such impertinence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.65,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Ah well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:01.08,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let it go for today. Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:10.31,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki... Thanks to\Nyour sacrifice, I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.94,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...and farewell forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go killing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.17,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.40,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:30.01,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Let us continue to protect the\Npeace on this planet together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.37,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:35.55,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.55,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:43.90,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.29,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.55,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to put this patch\Non Kuchiki's costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.14,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fix the costumes\Nand do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.98,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I want you to do\Nit again just like we just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be our\Nnext filming location.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.66,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Sokyoku Hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:20.45,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. No camera has ever\Nentered this sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.46,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's value\Nin filming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:26.90,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Are we pulling off the "Produced with full\Ncooperation from the famous" tactic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.75,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.97,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think, Ichigo?\NDoesn't it make you excited?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.42,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong\Nabout this whole film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.64,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, why am I the only one\Nwho's getting beaten up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.43,B2,ICHIGO (N),0000,0000,0000,,The explosions are\Ntoo powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.94,B2,ICHIGO (N),0000,0000,0000,,the attacks are precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.40,B2,ICHIGO (N),0000,0000,0000,,and I get shoved down from crazy\Nplaces without warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.95,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You did some great acting in\Nevery one of those scenes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I don't\Nhave a clue as to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,what the story of this\Nfilm is to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.44,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:03.25,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to cut and paste during\Nthe editing stage anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.66,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.96,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,we can just erase the sound\Nand dub over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.67,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,and we can do anything we\Nwant with CG and music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.89,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! You're not putting\Nany thought into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.34,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:19.14,B2,RANGIKI,0000,0000,0000,,Focusing too much on the script\Ncould cause problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.85,B2,RANGIKU (N),0000,0000,0000,,Take Shuhei's group\Nfor example.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.52,B2,RANGIKU (N),0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't finished\Nthe script yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.48,B2,RANGIKU (N),0000,0000,0000,,and now they are way\Nbehind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.11,B2,RANGIKU (N),0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori is so\Npissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.86,B2,RANGIKI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to\Nend up like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.10,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that sounds rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:36.92,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,When the script is late, it's the\Ncrew on the scene that suffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.46,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Muh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:38.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya! Your aim\Nis too accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.41,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a grudge against me,\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.46,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:53.50,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I decided it was necessary\Nin the pursuit of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How noble of you, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.79,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,We're letting our names\Nbe credited in this film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.55,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,By the Kuchiki Clan's honor, I cannot\Nallow any mistakes to be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Aargh! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.32,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.98,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,But Kurosaki, we've come\Nthis far into the filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Inoue, I can't\Ndo this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.26,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What're you afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.90,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So you got beat up\Nduring filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:27.83,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting yourself get discouraged\Nby something so trivial?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.50,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You're not confident about\Nlooking good on camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:36.92,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you afraid of getting beaten\Nup in the pursuit of reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.99,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have confidence\Nin your acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.83,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,make up for it with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.27,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not confident about\Nmaking it look real,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.59,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,think up some way to fake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:49.98,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're afraid of the schedule\Npressing down on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.36,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,do all your scenes in one take.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.82,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if no one else\Nbelieves in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.78,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,hold your head up high and\Nshout out your lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:01.36,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man I know\Nyou as, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.22,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's start filming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.05,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.01,B2,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.29,B2,REAPER GUARD,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.64,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! They found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:33.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean, Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.56,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Pack it up everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:37.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you didn't get a\Npermit to film here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.15,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.43,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be easier\Nto just do a guerrilla filming
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.53,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,than go through the hassle\Nof getting permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.91,B2,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.75,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.25,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:55.88,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.01,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.85,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.07,B2,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:09.85,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.34,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,No choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.32,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai! Hihio Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:28.09,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Just as I planned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.16,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That's going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:34.45,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They headed us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How is this "just as\Nyou planned it"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming from behind too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.09,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.03,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,By the Kuchiki Clan's honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:47.05,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow myself to\Nbe captured here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:51.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Your honor disappeared the moment\Nyou got involved with this film.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Byakuya! What're\Nyou going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:58.11,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai... Senbonzakura Kageyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.31,B2,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.73,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:19.74,B2,RUKIA (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so peace returns to the\NSoul Society thanks to the{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.75,B2,CREDITS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}Written by: Renji Abarai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.96,B2,RUKIA (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}efforts of young Ichigo Kurosaki,\Nwho blew himself up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.63,B2,Maid Cop,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}Maid Cop: Rukia Kuchiki \N Lovely Criminal: Rangiku Matsumoto {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.78,B2,RUKIA (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, we'd like to add that\Nthis story is a work of fiction{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:29.68,B2,RUKIA (N),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and is not associated with\Nany actual location.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.30,B2,CREDITS,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}Special Effects: Byakuya Kuchiki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.85,B2,Camera,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}Camera: Uryu Ishida \NGofer: Yasutora Sado
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:33.47,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your\Nsupport everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.64,B2,Directed by,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}Directed by: Renji Abarai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.65,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.49,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling it "Close Call\Nfor the Soul Society!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.86,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,The Film Festival Grand\NPrix is as good as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:47.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't have done this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There's a grand prix for\Nthis film festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:24.15,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It's been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:25.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:28.15,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,The Seireitei was destroyed\Nduring filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:32.59,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the grand prix money\Nwas used for the repairs instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But that was all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:36.31,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:40.35,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,We're making a movie too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:43.12,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid! Count me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:48.84,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And here I was going to\Nmake you the star, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.58,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then\NI might consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:00.92,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.21,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling it\N"Great Monster Hiyora"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:04.97,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,You damn baldy!